{"tid":374629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「帕卡」移向廣東　一號風球現正生效","createTime":"2017-08-26T01:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T01:51:34.000Z","uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40ae85b8b8189a240601e56a331028af65ab8ebe","tid":374629,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:46:58.000Z","msg":"一號戒備訊號現正生效。在上午8時，熱帶風暴「帕卡」集結在東沙之東南約490公里，預料向西北移動，時速約28公里，進入南海，並逐漸增強。天文台考慮日間發出1號戒備訊號。天文台續指，「帕卡」採取偏西北方向移向廣東西部，至於「帕卡」對本港的影響，需要視乎其強度及位置。<br />\n<br />\n天文台預測本港今日大致天晴，但有一兩陣驟雨。日間天氣酷熱，最高氣溫約33度。吹和緩東風，後轉吹東北風。展望未來一兩日風勢頗大及有狂風驟雨，下週中期天氣好轉。另外，天文台已發出酷熱天氣警告。<br />\n<br />\n又打到黎了，澳門準備好未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/114744/-%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3-%E5%B8%95%E5%8D%A1-%E7%A7%BB%E5%90%91%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1-%E4%B8%80%E8%99%9F%E9%A2%A8%E7%90%83%E7%8F%BE%E6%AD%A3%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F114744%2F-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E5%25B8%2595%25E5%258D%25A1-%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2599%259F%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2595%2588&d=yrJc84O7XcVjWbJJagXf9pzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=8c69306b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/114744/-%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3-%E5%B8%95%E5%8D%A1-%E7%A7%BB%E5%90%91%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1-%E4%B8%80%E8%99%9F%E9%A2%A8%E7%90%83%E7%8F%BE%E6%AD%A3%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88</a>"},{"pid":"ef5fe15a4de270004de904ef843c7da0a50b394a","tid":374629,"uid":129288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:47:56.000Z","msg":"天滅澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bcff9763ca644d7701e706f8d486bd52d417fb","tid":374629,"uid":45494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201